column5: I have rented a cottage with the family on Leonard Lake, off 118 in Muskoka. Anyone fished it?  Anything worthwhile. Wigler
Stayed here on one occasion for a weekend.  Only caught small mouth, nothing big. It was pretty tough with artificials, had more luck using live worms.

I believe I was there once a long time ago for a day in the fall. It was one of the lakes stocked with Rainbow Trout, so we went to check it out. We did not catch anything from my recollection.  It was stocked in 2009, 2010, 2012, 2014 and 2016 so you never know.
